LISTEN, TROY, TROY, JUST
GIVE US A LITTLE TIME, OKAY?

435
00:25:27,827 --> 00:25:29,795
LITTLE MORE TIME, OKAY?

436
00:25:32,715 --> 00:25:35,217
HEY, LUCY.
LUCY, COULD I GET A--

437
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:39,221
BITCH.

438
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:44,893
( laughs )
THE KING IS BACK, BABY.

439
00:25:44,894 --> 00:25:47,897
MOTHERFUCK, THE DROUGHT IS OVER,
AND THE KING IS BACK!

440
00:25:47,897 --> 00:25:50,182
YOU'RE DISTURBED.

441
00:25:52,685 --> 00:25:54,687
- THIS IS DISTURBING.
- JESUS!

442
00:25:54,687 --> 00:25:58,691
YEAH, 40-TO-ONE SHOT.
YEAH, $6,300.  YEAH.

443
00:25:58,691 --> 00:26:01,193
THE OLD PSYCHIC DYKES
IS BACK, BABY!

444
00:26:01,193 --> 00:26:02,694
I GUESS YOU'RE RIGHT.
LISTEN...

445
00:26:02,695 --> 00:26:05,197
- ( laughing )
- HEY, HEY-- PUT THE WAD AWAY.

446
00:26:05,197 --> 00:26:07,199
PUT IT AWAY.

447
00:26:08,617 --> 00:26:10,619
SO, DID YOU, UH...

448
00:26:10,619 --> 00:26:12,253
DID YOU HEAR ABOUT LOMAX?

449
00:26:12,254 --> 00:26:15,257
YEAH, I HEARD THEY GOT WHACKED
IN HOLLYWOOD, HANSEN, MAN.

450
00:26:15,257 --> 00:26:18,260
IT'S BAD KARMA COMING BACK
ON THOSE GUYS, MAN.

451
00:26:22,381 --> 00:26:24,433
- LUCY!
- SHE'S NOT GONNA COME OVER HERE.

452
00:26:24,433 --> 00:26:25,934
SHE IS--

453
00:26:25,935 --> 00:26:28,437
REMEMBER THOSE SUITS
THOSE GUYS HAD?

454
00:26:28,437 --> 00:26:30,439
- BEAUTIFUL ITALIAN NUMBERS.
- YEAH, YEAH, YEAH--

455
00:26:30,439 --> 00:26:34,309
- HEY!
- HEY, DARLIN'. A ROUND ON ME, PLEASE.

456
00:26:34,310 --> 00:26:38,314
- MY PLEASURE... DETECTIVE.
- THANK YOU.

457
00:26:39,732 --> 00:26:42,284
JACK.  JACK.
WOMEN ARE EASY.

458
00:26:42,284 --> 00:26:44,619
YEAH, UNLESS
YOU TRY TO TOUCH 'EM.

459
00:26:44,620 --> 00:26:47,656
<i>HEY, YOU KNOW,</i>
<i>I WAS THINKING...</i>

460
00:26:47,656 --> 00:26:50,325
THOSE GUYS HAD
A PRETTY GOOD THING GOIN'.

461
00:26:50,326 --> 00:26:52,211
<i>I MEAN, THEY DID.</i>
<i>NO, NO, NO, NO.</i>

462
00:26:52,211 --> 00:26:54,213
THEY-THEY TOOK IT TOO FAR.

463
00:26:54,213 --> 00:26:55,714
THEY WERE GREEDY, BUT...

464
00:26:55,714 --> 00:26:57,499
THEY HAD A NICE THING GOIN'.

465
00:26:57,499 --> 00:27:01,135
- HANSEN, MAN, WAS INTO
SOME SERIOUS SHIT, THOUGH. - <i>NO, I KNOW.</i>

466
00:27:01,136 --> 00:27:04,556
BUT DID YOU EVER WONDER
WHAT SHIT EXACTLY HE WAS INTO?

467
00:27:06,058 --> 00:27:08,060
YEAH, I WONDERED.

468
00:27:09,428 --> 00:27:12,264
THAT'S NOT OUR CASE, JACK.

469
00:27:15,401 --> 00:27:17,736
I'M GONNA GO
TAKE A PISS.

470
00:27:21,657 --> 00:27:23,659
I DARE YOU.

471
00:27:27,663 --> 00:27:30,165
LUCY, KEEP THE CHANGE.

472
00:27:30,165 --> 00:27:31,666
HEY, THANKS A LOT.

473
00:27:31,667 --> 00:27:34,169
YOU KNOW, I HAVEN'T SEEN
YOU AROUND FOR A WHILE.

474
00:27:34,169 --> 00:27:36,287
I'VE BEEN, UH, BUSY?

475
00:27:42,795 --> 00:27:44,596
<i>( squishes )</i>

476
00:27:44,596 --> 00:27:48,099
JESUS CHRIST!
I TOLD YOU TO PICK UP AFTER THE FUCKING DOG.

477
00:27:50,102 --> 00:27:53,605
WOODY, I TOLD YOU
TO GO OUTSIDE.

478
00:27:53,605 --> 00:27:56,608
- HEY, IT'S GOOD LUCK.
- YEAH, RIGHT.

479
00:27:56,608 --> 00:27:59,143
<i>( TV playing )</i>

480
00:28:00,863 --> 00:28:02,865
SO?

481
00:28:04,700 --> 00:28:07,536
HOW WAS YOUR DAY
AT THE OFFICE?

482
00:28:09,538 --> 00:28:12,374
DID YOU JUST ASK ME
HOW MY DAY AT THE OFFICE WAS?

483
00:28:12,374 --> 00:28:15,043
YES.

484
00:28:16,795 --> 00:28:18,797
( sighs )

485
00:28:18,797 --> 00:28:21,299
MY DAY AT THE OFFICE
SUCKED, HELENA.

486
00:28:21,300 --> 00:28:23,468
JUST LIKE IT HAS
SINCE THE FIRST DAY I MET YOU.

487
00:28:26,972 --> 00:28:28,974
WHAT IS THIS?

488
00:28:28,974 --> 00:28:31,476
IT'S DINNER.

489
00:28:31,477 --> 00:28:33,479
YOU KNOW WHAT?

490
00:28:33,479 --> 00:28:36,482
FORGET IT.

491
00:28:36,482 --> 00:28:38,984
FORGET IT.  YOU KNOW,
I WAS TRYING TO BE NICE--

492
00:28:38,984 --> 00:28:40,485
BUT, WHATEVER.

493
00:28:40,486 --> 00:28:42,488
NO, NO, NO.
HEY, I'M SORRY.

494
00:28:42,488 --> 00:28:44,406
I'M SORRY, IT IS NICE.

495
00:28:44,406 --> 00:28:47,242
<i>IT'S VERY NICE.</i>
<i>I JUST--</i>

496
00:28:47,242 --> 00:28:49,244
I'M JUST A LITTLE CONFUSED,
THAT'S ALL.

497
00:28:49,244 --> 00:28:52,163
I JUST DON'T UNDERSTAND
WHY SOMEONE WOULD JUST BE

498
00:28:52,164 --> 00:28:54,115
DUMB LIKE YOU ARE.

499
00:28:54,116 --> 00:28:55,867
<i>I MEAN...</i>

500
00:28:55,868 --> 00:28:58,871
HERE I COME TO YOU
AND I HAVE INFORMATION

501
00:28:58,871 --> 00:29:02,758
THAT COULD POSSIBLY HELP
YOU GET THAT PROMOTION

502
00:29:02,758 --> 00:29:05,177
THAT YOU'VE BEEN
WAITING FOR FOREVER.

503
00:29:06,545 --> 00:29:08,129
I'M SORRY.  I'M SORRY.

504
00:29:08,130 --> 00:29:10,882
BUT, YOU KNOW WHAT?  FORGET IT.
YOU DON'T WANT IT.

505
00:29:14,019 --> 00:29:16,221
CAN--  CAN I TURN OFF
"MR. HAPPY"?

506
00:29:20,225 --> 00:29:22,727
GENTLY.

507
00:29:23,729 --> 00:29:25,731
( turns TV off )

508
00:29:29,068 --> 00:29:31,203
OKAY... SHOOT.

509
00:29:31,203 --> 00:29:33,705
<i>WHAT IS IT?</i>

510
00:29:33,705 --> 00:29:35,206
WELL...

511
00:29:35,207 --> 00:29:38,126
REMEMBER THE FRIENDS
I TOLD YOU ABOUT? MISHA AND LEXI?

512
00:29:38,127 --> 00:29:40,913
- VAGUELY.
- <i>THEY WERE LIVING</i> <i>WITH THESE TWO RUSSIANS,</i>

513
00:29:40,913 --> 00:29:44,716
AND THEY WERE PLANNING
TO HOLD UP A CASINO.

514
00:29:47,886 --> 00:29:50,255
THEY <i>WERE</i> PLANNING...?

515
00:29:50,255 --> 00:29:54,142
THE PEOPLE THAT THEY
WERE PLANNING IT WITH WERE THESE TWO COPS.

516
00:29:54,143 --> 00:29:57,012
TWO DEAD COPS.

517
00:29:57,012 --> 00:29:59,097
- ( chuckles )
- HUH?

518
00:29:59,098 --> 00:30:01,483
- <i>LOMAX AND HANSEN?</i>
- THAT'S SOMETHING, RIGHT?

519
00:30:01,483 --> 00:30:04,936
YEAH, THAT'S SOMETHING.
THAT'S SOMETHING.

520
00:30:04,937 --> 00:30:06,438
- YEAH, THAT'S--
- <i>THANK YOU?</i>

521
00:30:06,438 --> 00:30:09,908
- YEAH, THANK YOU, THANK YOU.
- 'CAUSE I KNOW IT.

522
00:30:12,578 --> 00:30:15,447
- ( grunting )
- Jack: 60 FOR US AND 40 FOR YOU!

523
00:30:15,447 --> 00:30:18,032
HEY, HEY!
WATCH THE HOOD ORNAMENT!

524
00:30:18,033 --> 00:30:21,419
60-- 40!

525
00:30:22,788 --> 00:30:25,590
KICK ASS, BARETTA.

526
00:30:28,377 --> 00:30:31,296
- USE THAT HOOD.
- ( Sergei speaking Russian )

527
00:30:33,298 --> 00:30:36,134
COME HERE!

528
00:30:36,135 --> 00:30:38,554
ALL RIGHT, HOLD ON.

529
00:30:40,055 --> 00:30:41,556
ALL RIGHT.

530
00:30:44,026 --> 00:30:46,311
ALL RIGHT, I GOT HIM.

531
00:30:46,311 --> 00:30:49,781
WHAT YOU ARE TRYING TO DO?
SEDUCE ME?

532
00:30:49,781 --> 00:30:52,116
Jack:
<i>MY FINAL OFFER, 60-40.</i>

533
00:30:53,035 --> 00:30:55,954
LICK MY RUSSIAN BALLS.

534
00:30:57,456 --> 00:30:59,458
YOU KNOW WHAT,
RUSSIAN?

535
00:30:59,458 --> 00:31:01,460
I DON'T LIKE THE TONE
OF YOUR VOICE.

536
00:31:01,460 --> 00:31:03,662
I DON'T EITHER.

537
00:31:03,662 --> 00:31:07,499
- <i>I REALLY DON'T.</i>
- CALL FOR BACKUP, JACK? OR WE SHOOT THEM HERE?

538
00:31:07,499 --> 00:31:09,000
NO, WE SHOULD GIVE THEM
A 10-COUNT.

539
00:31:09,001 --> 00:31:12,421
- ONE, TWO--
- THREE, SEVEN, 10.

540
00:31:12,421 --> 00:31:14,389
- SHUT UP!  SHUT THE--
- 10.

541
00:31:14,389 --> 00:31:17,008
- ALL RIGHT,
YOU HAVE A DEAL. - WHAT?

542
00:31:17,009 --> 00:31:20,012
- YOU HAVE A DEAL.
- WE GOT A DEAL.

543
00:31:20,012 --> 00:31:23,015
WE GOT A DEAL.
BEAUTIFUL.

544
00:31:25,517 --> 00:31:29,020
- 10:00.
- TOMORROW NIGHT AT THE PUSSYCAT.

545
00:31:32,524 --> 00:31:34,742
CUNT!
THIS IS FOR YOU, EH?

546
00:31:35,744 --> 00:31:37,746
( spits )

547
00:31:42,167 --> 00:31:45,170
- <i>L'AMOUR.</i>
- "L'AMOR"

548
00:31:45,170 --> 00:31:49,674
- NOT L'AMOR.
<i>AMOR</i> IS SPANISH. - YEAH.

549
00:31:49,675 --> 00:31:52,177
- <i>L'AMOUR.</i>  SAY IT.
- <i>L'AMOUR.</i>

550
00:31:52,177 --> 00:31:54,179
- <i>L'AMOUR.</i>
- <i>L'AMOUR.</i>

551
00:31:54,179 --> 00:31:56,681
YOU SAY IT MUCH BETTER.

552
00:31:56,682 --> 00:32:00,185
<i>L'AMOUR.</i>
SAY IT AGAIN.

553
00:32:00,185 --> 00:32:02,187
<i>L'AMOUR.</i>

554
00:32:03,689 --> 00:32:06,191
YOU SURE YOU DON'T
WANT TO COME?

555
00:32:06,191 --> 00:32:07,692
NO.

556
00:32:10,696 --> 00:32:13,198
YOU'RE NOT GONNA
CALL DARREN, ARE YOU?

557
00:32:13,198 --> 00:32:15,200
DARREN WHO?

558
00:32:17,202 --> 00:32:20,705
I'M JUST GONNA WATCH THE ROACHES
CRAWL AROUND THE ROOM.

559
00:32:21,707 --> 00:32:23,709
I PROMISE.

560
00:32:27,713 --> 00:32:30,716
I'M FINE.
I CAN BE ALONE.

561
00:32:32,134 --> 00:32:36,638
<i>♪ I'M FEELING SO LOST ♪</i>

562
00:32:36,638 --> 00:32:40,642
<i>♪ I CAN'T SEE</i>
<i>WHERE I'M GOING ♪</i>

563
00:32:44,062 --> 00:32:47,348
<i>♪ IS THERE</i>
<i>SOMETHING AHEAD? ♪</i>

564
00:32:48,934 --> 00:32:53,355
<i>♪ DID I LEAVE</i>
<i>WHAT'S IMPORTANT BEHIND? ♪</i>

565
00:32:56,358 --> 00:33:03,281
<i>♪ MY BODY'S SO TIRED</i>
<i>I AM ACHING DOWN TO MY SOUL ♪</i>

566
00:33:03,282 --> 00:33:06,285
<i>♪ CAN'T HOLD ON</i>
<i>CAN'T LET GO ♪</i>

567
00:33:06,285 --> 00:33:11,790
<i>♪ WHILE I'M SPINNING</i>
<i>OUT OF CONTROL... ♪</i>

568
00:33:11,790 --> 00:33:14,292
<i>( doorbell rings )</i>

569
00:33:14,293 --> 00:33:20,599
<i>♪ AND LOVE PASSES BY</i>
<i>LIKE SCENES FROM A MOVIE ♪</i>

570
00:33:20,599 --> 00:33:24,603
<i>♪ TO AN ENDING</i>
<i>THAT I NEVER PLANNED. ♪</i>

571
00:33:26,855 --> 00:33:29,357
- HI.
- HI.

572
00:33:31,643 --> 00:33:33,895
YOU COMING BACK?

573
00:33:36,398 --> 00:33:38,733
I DON'T KNOW.

574
00:33:52,914 --> 00:33:57,418
- HELENA!
- I'M WATCHING "WHEEL."

575
00:33:57,419 --> 00:33:59,421
Pat Sajak:
<i>There are five Os.</i>

576
00:33:59,421 --> 00:34:02,924
<i>( cheering )</i>

577
00:34:12,317 --> 00:34:14,819
- WHAT'S WITH YOU?
- NOTHING.

578
00:34:14,820 --> 00:34:19,991
WHAT?
I'M IN A GOOD MOOD. I CAN'T BE IN A GOOD MOOD?

579
00:34:19,991 --> 00:34:22,276
I GUESS.

580
00:34:23,945 --> 00:34:27,915
KIND OF CREEPY,
THOUGH.

581
00:34:27,916 --> 00:34:31,502
- <i>( TV continues )</i>
- I'M GONNA--

582
00:34:31,503 --> 00:34:36,007
- <i>UH-UH-UH!</i>
- I'M JUST TURNING DOWN THE SOUND, OKAY?

583
00:34:41,263 --> 00:34:44,633
- <i>( chuckles )</i>
- MMM.

584
00:34:47,135 --> 00:34:50,771
YOU, UH-- YOU THINK
IT COULD STILL WORK?

585
00:34:50,772 --> 00:34:53,191
WHAT WORK?

586
00:34:53,191 --> 00:34:55,193
US!  US COULD STILL WORK?

587
00:34:55,193 --> 00:34:59,030
I MEAN, IF WE HAD
A NICER PLACE TO LIVE, LITTLE MORE MONEY

588
00:34:59,030 --> 00:35:01,649
<i>TO TAKE THE PRESSURE OFF.</i>

589
00:35:01,650 --> 00:35:04,486
YOU KNOW.  I MEAN,
MAYBE IF WE JUST TRIED A LITTLE HARDER.

590
00:35:04,486 --> 00:35:07,789
YOU ON ECSTASY
OR SOMETHING?

591
00:35:14,162 --> 00:35:16,631
SO, WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH THE RUSSIANS?

592
00:35:19,634 --> 00:35:22,086
DON'T WORRY
YOUR LITTLE HEAD ABOUT IT.

593
00:35:22,087 --> 00:35:25,340
- YOU'RE GOING TO
ARREST THEM, RIGHT? - WE'RE KEEPING TABS ON THEM.

594
00:35:25,340 --> 00:35:27,842
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

595
00:35:27,843 --> 00:35:29,845
I MEAN,
THERE ARE TWO DEAD COPS,

596
00:35:29,845 --> 00:35:32,848
AND WE HAVE REASON TO BELIEVE
THESE TWO RUSSIAN GENTLEMEN

597
00:35:32,848 --> 00:35:34,850
WERE INVOLVED IN SOME WAY,
SHAPE OR FORM,

598
00:35:34,850 --> 00:35:37,819
SO NOW IT'S JUST
WATCH AND WAIT.

599
00:35:37,819 --> 00:35:40,738
BUT YOU ARE GOING
TO ARREST THEM, RIGHT?

600
00:35:41,740 --> 00:35:43,742
( yawns )

601
00:35:46,611 --> 00:35:48,996
OH, YEAH.  YEAH.

602
00:35:48,997 --> 00:35:52,000
<i>YEAH, WE WILL...</i>
<i>WHEN IT'S TIME.</i>

603
00:35:57,005 --> 00:36:00,008
WOODY, DID YOU SEE ME YAWN?

604
00:36:01,510 --> 00:36:04,012
I DIDN'T YAWN, DID I?

605
00:36:06,298 --> 00:36:09,301
HE'S A FUCKING
LITTLE LIAR.

606
00:36:09,301 --> 00:36:10,302
I KNOW HOW HE LIES.

607
00:36:10,302 --> 00:36:12,804
I KNOW WHEN HE LIES,
HE YAWNS.

608
00:36:12,804 --> 00:36:15,640
AND HE YAWNED... REAL BIG.
HE'S A WEAK LITTLE SHIT.

609
00:36:15,640 --> 00:36:18,059
HE PROBABLY DIDN'T EVEN FUCKING
TALK TO THE RUSSIANS.

610
00:36:18,059 --> 00:36:19,560
MAYBE HE DID.

611
00:36:19,561 --> 00:36:22,864
MAYBE HE TRIED
TO SCREW YOU OVER-- LIKE THE REST OF US.

612
00:36:25,367 --> 00:36:26,901
NO...

613
00:36:26,902 --> 00:36:29,454
IT'S A LOT OF MONEY.

614
00:36:31,957 --> 00:36:34,409
HE BROUGHT ME
FLOWERS YESTERDAY.

615
00:36:36,962 --> 00:36:39,497
- AND CANDY.
- ( scoffs )

616
00:36:39,498 --> 00:36:42,000
TALKING ABOUT A WHOLE NEW
FUCKING LIFE.

617
00:36:43,418 --> 00:36:47,555
I BET YOU
THAT'S WHAT HE'S DOING. LITTLE FUCKING WEASEL.

618
00:36:47,556 --> 00:36:49,641
YOU'RE SO MUCH SMARTER
THAN HIM.

619
00:36:49,641 --> 00:36:52,143
- I AM SMARTER THAN HIM!
- YES, YOU ARE.

620
00:36:53,144 --> 00:36:56,730
I WILL NAIL HIS ASS
TO THE WALL.

621
00:36:56,731 --> 00:37:01,235
<i>( music playing,</i>
<i>singing, chatting )</i>

622
00:37:01,236 --> 00:37:03,438
Troy:
<i>THE RESPONSE TIME</i> <i>VARIES.</i>

623
00:37:03,438 --> 00:37:05,940
I'VE SEEN TWO MINUTES.
I'VE SEEN 10.

624
00:37:05,941 --> 00:37:08,443
SO YOU NEED
TO BE PATCHED IN WITH THE POLICE SCANNER.

625
00:37:08,443 --> 00:37:10,661
ANY DIVERSIONS
WILL BE APPRECIATED.

626
00:37:10,662 --> 00:37:13,164
- THAT'S NO PROBLEM.
A PIECE OF CAKE, RIGHT? - Dykes: <i>YEAH.</i>

627
00:37:13,164 --> 00:37:16,000
Yuri:
<i>SERGEI AND I STORM IN</i> <i>DURING THE BLACKOUT,</i>

628
00:37:16,001 --> 00:37:19,504
HIT THE GUARDS WITH
FLASHBANGS AND TEAR GAS.

629
00:37:19,504 --> 00:37:22,256
I'LL BEEP YOU THE SECOND
SECURITY ENTERS. WE'LL BLOW IT,

630
00:37:22,257 --> 00:37:24,759
AND THE LIGHTS GO OUT
IN THE CASINO.

631
00:37:24,759 --> 00:37:26,761
ALL RIGHT.

632
00:37:28,263 --> 00:37:30,765
YOU KNOW, GUYS,
CALL ME CRAZY...

633
00:37:32,767 --> 00:37:35,269
BUT I WANT
MY STRIPPERS TO STRIP,

634
00:37:35,270 --> 00:37:37,105
NOT FUCKING SING.

635
00:37:37,105 --> 00:37:41,559
♪ WHY HAS IT BEEN SO LONG? ♪

636
00:37:41,560 --> 00:37:46,364
♪ I LONG TO BE THE ONE ♪

637
00:37:46,364 --> 00:37:51,569
♪ YOU HAVE A HANDLE ON. ♪

638
00:37:58,710 --> 00:38:01,713
( panting )

639
00:38:01,713 --> 00:38:04,716
- LUCY.
- COME ON, YOU USED TO BE BETTER THAN ME!

640
00:38:04,716 --> 00:38:08,219
I KNOW.
IT'S JUST A LITTLE BIT FUCKED UP RIGHT NOW.

641
00:38:08,219 --> 00:38:11,805
SO, COME ON,
HOW ABOUT IT? HELP AN OLD PAL?

642
00:38:11,806 --> 00:38:14,475
OH, YEAH.
YOU DON'T CALL ME FOR A YEAR,

643
00:38:14,476 --> 00:38:16,594
AND NOW YOU WANT ME
TO DO YOUR DIRTY WORK, RIGHT?

644
00:38:16,595 --> 00:38:19,264
COME ON,
I THOUGHT YOU WOULD LOVE TO PISS OFF JACK!

645
00:38:19,264 --> 00:38:22,267
- BESIDES--
- DON'T MENTION STATEN.

646
00:38:22,267 --> 00:38:24,769
COME ON.  I AM
PERSONALLY THE ONE

647
00:38:24,769 --> 00:38:27,271
WHO PULLED YOU
OUT OF THE RIVER IN STATEN.

648
00:38:27,272 --> 00:38:29,274
ALL RIGHT, LOOK--

649
00:38:29,274 --> 00:38:32,277
AFTER THIS,
NO MORE NEW JERSEY.

650
00:38:32,277 --> 00:38:34,279
AND I'M NOT GONNA TOUCH HIM.

