1087
01:06:55,111 --> 01:06:58,147
ISN'T IT JUST EASIER
TO TAKE THEM OUT?

1088
01:06:58,148 --> 01:07:00,700
WHAT'S WITH ALL
THE QUESTIONS? COME ON.

1089
01:07:00,700 --> 01:07:02,785
I'M JUST ASKING.

1090
01:07:02,786 --> 01:07:05,405
WE WON'T HAVE ENOUGH TIME
IF WE'RE RUNNING.

1091
01:07:05,405 --> 01:07:08,040
SO, AFTER THE HIT,
WE'LL PROBABLY HAVE

1092
01:07:08,041 --> 01:07:10,209
TWO TO 10 MINUTES
TO GET OUT OF THE CASINO.

1093
01:07:10,210 --> 01:07:14,247
AND ANOTHER TWO HOURS
TO GET BEYOND THE CITY LIMITS.

1094
01:07:14,247 --> 01:07:16,749
- WHO'S DRIVING
THE RENT-A-CAR? - I'LL DRIVE.

1095
01:07:24,174 --> 01:07:26,176
HEY.

1096
01:07:39,689 --> 01:07:42,191
GOOD MORNING.

1097
01:07:43,193 --> 01:07:45,278
<i>( door creaks )</i>

1098
01:07:47,280 --> 01:07:49,332
Helena: HEY.

1099
01:07:50,333 --> 01:07:52,835
- HEY.
- HI!

1100
01:07:57,340 --> 01:07:59,842
WE'RE STILL
DOING THIS, RIGHT?

1101
01:08:00,844 --> 01:08:04,347
- RIGHT?
- Misha: ARE WE?

1102
01:08:04,347 --> 01:08:07,350
YOU GUYS TALKED ME INTO THIS.
YOU BETTER BE DOING THIS.

1103
01:08:08,351 --> 01:08:11,354
LET'S DO THIS.

1104
01:08:11,354 --> 01:08:13,856
- I'M READY.
- LET'S GO.

1105
01:08:32,709 --> 01:08:34,794
Troy:
<i>YOU KNOW WHAT?</i>

1106
01:08:34,794 --> 01:08:36,662
IT'S PRETTY CROWDED
DOWN HERE.

1107
01:08:36,663 --> 01:08:39,666
IN ABOUT AN HOUR OR SO,
IT'S GONNA BE PACKED.

1108
01:08:39,666 --> 01:08:42,168
SO LET'S SWITCH CAMERAS 14
AND NINE TO THE FLOOR.

1109
01:08:42,168 --> 01:08:44,170
GET SOME MORE EYES
DOWN HERE.

1110
01:08:52,178 --> 01:08:53,812
( beeps )

1111
01:09:04,324 --> 01:09:06,326
GOOD MORNING!

1112
01:09:06,326 --> 01:09:09,329
- ( laughing )
- IT'S 6:00 ALREADY?

1113
01:09:09,329 --> 01:09:11,831
- GOD.
- OH, YEAH.

1114
01:09:11,831 --> 01:09:13,999
- LET ME HAVE SOME OF THAT.
- HERE YOU GO.

1115
01:09:16,703 --> 01:09:19,205
- THANK YOU.
- YOU'RE WELCOME.

1116
01:09:23,126 --> 01:09:26,629
- GOOD COFFEE.
- THANK YOU.

1117
01:09:36,222 --> 01:09:40,226
( groans )
LISTEN, MAN, I GOTTA GO.

1118
01:09:41,227 --> 01:09:43,028
I KNOW THE FEELING.

1119
01:10:54,267 --> 01:10:56,936
STAY HERE,
I'LL BE BACK.

1120
01:10:56,936 --> 01:10:59,521
- TAKE CARE, OKAY?
- GO!

1121
01:11:14,787 --> 01:11:16,872
( beeps )

1122
01:11:26,416 --> 01:11:28,751
OKAY.

1123
01:11:28,751 --> 01:11:30,886
NUMBER-- 420.

1124
01:11:30,887 --> 01:11:33,723
- HOW MUCH TIME DO WE HAVE?
- <i>10:30, NO LATER.</i>

1125
01:11:36,426 --> 01:11:38,394
OKAY.

1126
01:11:38,394 --> 01:11:41,096
VINNIE!
I GOT SOMETHING FOR YOU.

1127
01:11:41,097 --> 01:11:43,933
VINNIE WENT HOME SICK.

1128
01:11:45,435 --> 01:11:46,819
WHO ARE YOU?

1129
01:11:46,819 --> 01:11:49,855
KEVIN SHEPELA.

1130
01:11:49,856 --> 01:11:52,358
THIS WHOLE SECURITY TEAM
NEEDS TO GET MORE ORGANIZED.

1131
01:11:52,358 --> 01:11:55,411
- YOU ALWAYS LEAVE
THE SAFE OPEN? - YEAH, WE DO.

1132
01:11:57,246 --> 01:11:59,364
DID THAT HAPPEN
ON THE FORCE?

1133
01:11:59,365 --> 01:12:01,867
NAH, I WAS HELPING
SOME ILLEGAL

1134
01:12:01,868 --> 01:12:04,754
FIX A FLAT TIRE,
AND THE JACK SNAPPED.

1135
01:12:04,754 --> 01:12:07,673
- OUCH.
- YEAH... OUCH.

1136
01:12:17,433 --> 01:12:20,936
UH... STACIE
AND ARCADIA.  OKAY.

1137
01:12:25,274 --> 01:12:27,309
( sparking )

1138
01:12:31,064 --> 01:12:33,366
- <i>( door opens )</i>
- HEY!

1139
01:12:33,366 --> 01:12:35,868
- HI.
- EXCUSE ME.

1140
01:12:40,289 --> 01:12:43,625
- ARE YOU GUYS
STACIE AND ARCADIA? - YEAH.

1141
01:12:43,626 --> 01:12:46,545
- NICE TO MEET YOU.
- ( sparking )

1142
01:12:53,670 --> 01:12:56,172
WAIT, WE CAN'T FIT
THEM BOTH IN HERE.

1143
01:12:56,172 --> 01:12:57,923
WE HAVE TO.

1144
01:12:57,924 --> 01:13:00,426
SHIT!
IT'S IN HER POCKET. I SAW IT.

1145
01:13:01,427 --> 01:13:03,929
IT'S RIGHT THERE.
TAKE THIS.

1146
01:13:07,433 --> 01:13:09,435
YOU GOT IT?

1147
01:13:12,572 --> 01:13:15,074
OH, GOSH.  SHIT.

1148
01:13:15,074 --> 01:13:17,576
JUST BE CALM.

1149
01:13:18,695 --> 01:13:20,697
CAN YOU SEE MY GUN?

1150
01:13:20,697 --> 01:13:23,199
- WHAT'S YOUR NAME?
- ARCADIA.

1151
01:13:26,703 --> 01:13:28,121
SHIT.

1152
01:13:28,121 --> 01:13:31,124
- I THINK THEY'RE LOOKING.
- NO, THEY'RE NOT.

1153
01:13:31,124 --> 01:13:34,127
I FEEL LIKE
I'M GONNA PUKE. I <i>AM</i> GOING TO PUKE.

1154
01:13:34,127 --> 01:13:37,130
- HI.
- HI.  WHO WAS SHE?

1155
01:13:45,938 --> 01:13:48,140
CAN YOU SEE MY GUN?

1156
01:13:48,141 --> 01:13:49,859
FUCK.

1157
01:13:50,727 --> 01:13:53,229
WE ALL RIGHT?

1158
01:13:53,229 --> 01:13:56,232
THERE'S A SECURITY GUARD
FOLLOWING US.

1159
01:13:56,232 --> 01:13:58,534
FUCK.
LET'S JUST FORGET THIS. LET'S FORGET THIS.

1160
01:13:58,534 --> 01:14:00,786
NO, WAIT, WAIT.
DON'T LOOK BACK.

1161
01:14:00,787 --> 01:14:03,823
- I CAN'T DO THIS.
- YES, YOU CAN. YES, YOU CAN.

1162
01:14:03,823 --> 01:14:05,825
- I'M GONNA THROW UP.
- YOU CAN.

1163
01:14:05,825 --> 01:14:08,661
- I CAN'T DO THIS.
- HERE IT IS.  HERE'S THE DOOR.

1164
01:14:08,661 --> 01:14:11,130
HERE'S THE ELEVATOR.
THIS IS THE DOOR.

1165
01:14:19,555 --> 01:14:21,056
( buzzes )

1166
01:14:21,057 --> 01:14:23,059
COME ON, TRY AGAIN.
THE OTHER SIDE.

1167
01:14:24,560 --> 01:14:26,929
- LADIES.
- HI.

1168
01:14:30,433 --> 01:14:32,151
SHIT.

1169
01:14:32,151 --> 01:14:34,653
NEW HERE, HUH?

1170
01:14:34,654 --> 01:14:36,656
- YEAH.
- YEAH, STACIE.

1171
01:14:36,656 --> 01:14:38,658
STACIE.

1172
01:14:39,659 --> 01:14:42,662
- THIS WAY.
- ( beeps )

1173
01:14:42,662 --> 01:14:45,665
- TOMMY.
- TOMMY!

1174
01:14:45,665 --> 01:14:47,917
- THANKS.
- TAKE IT EASY.

1175
01:14:52,004 --> 01:14:55,123
- I GOTTA GO
TAKE A LEAK, MAN. - BE MY GUEST.

1176
01:15:00,213 --> 01:15:01,714
( buzzes )

1177
01:15:01,714 --> 01:15:03,932
DON'T MOVE!

1178
01:15:03,933 --> 01:15:08,637
( alarm blaring )

1179
01:15:08,638 --> 01:15:11,774
- <i>DROP YOUR WEAPON!</i>
- YOU DROP IT OR I'M GONNA BLOW HIS HEAD OFF--

1180
01:15:15,278 --> 01:15:17,280
COPY THAT.

1181
01:15:25,488 --> 01:15:27,790
WHAT HAPPENED?
OH MY GOD!

1182
01:15:27,790 --> 01:15:30,459
SHE'S GONNA SHOOT ME, MAN!
DON'T BE A HERO!

1183
01:15:30,459 --> 01:15:32,577
<i>THROW DOWN</i>
<i>YOUR GODDAMN GUN!</i>

1184
01:15:36,382 --> 01:15:38,250
<i>( alarm continues )</i>

1185
01:15:52,849 --> 01:15:56,068
WHAT IS HE DOING?
HELENA!

1186
01:16:11,784 --> 01:16:13,535
FUCK...

1187
01:16:18,708 --> 01:16:20,209
OH MY GOD.

1188
01:16:20,209 --> 01:16:21,960
COME ON, HELP ME.

1189
01:16:21,961 --> 01:16:24,096
- LET'S GET THE HELL OUT.
- NO, FORGET IT!

1190
01:16:25,097 --> 01:16:26,965
( growls )

1191
01:16:26,966 --> 01:16:30,052
HEY, HEY, HEY.
BACK TO THE PLAN.

1192
01:16:30,052 --> 01:16:32,054
I NEED YOU TO HIT ME.
I NEED YOU TO HIT ME.

1193
01:16:32,054 --> 01:16:34,773
NOT TOO HARD,
BUT I NEED YOU TO HIT ME-- ( screams )

1194
01:16:37,810 --> 01:16:39,812
FUCK!

1195
01:16:43,733 --> 01:16:47,119
HELP ME.

1196
01:16:47,119 --> 01:16:49,121
<i>( gunshot )</i>

1197
01:16:52,792 --> 01:16:54,660
COME ON!

1198
01:16:55,962 --> 01:16:59,131
FIRE!  THERE'S A FIRE!

1199
01:17:20,319 --> 01:17:22,354
LEXI, GO!

1200
01:17:22,355 --> 01:17:24,440
DRIVE!

1201
01:17:24,440 --> 01:17:25,941
GO, GO, GO!

1202
01:17:25,942 --> 01:17:28,411
WE KILLED
A FUCKING GUY! DRIVE!

1203
01:17:28,411 --> 01:17:30,529
WHAT HAPPENED?
WHERE'S THE MONEY?

1204
01:17:30,529 --> 01:17:33,498
- NO ONE WAS
SUPPOSED TO GET HURT! - <i>HE WOULD'VE SHOT YOU.</i>

1205
01:17:33,499 --> 01:17:35,784
- <i>SHIT!</i>
- OH MY GOD.  OH MY GOD!

1206
01:17:35,785 --> 01:17:39,171
- <i>HOW MANY MINUTES</i>
<i>UNTIL THE COPS SHOW UP?</i> - FOUR, I DON'T KNOW.

1207
01:17:39,171 --> 01:17:40,922
POOR TROY.
YOU HIT HIM REALLY HARD.

1208
01:17:40,923 --> 01:17:43,875
- Helena: <i>FUCK TROY!</i>
- TROY?  I SAW HIM GET INTO HIS CAR.

1209
01:17:43,876 --> 01:17:46,545
- WHAT?
- I JUST SAW HIM GET INTO HIS CAR.

1210
01:17:46,545 --> 01:17:49,214
HE WENT THAT WAY.

1211
01:17:49,215 --> 01:17:51,634
- <i>TURN AROUND.</i>
- <i>TURN THE CAR AROUND!</i>

1212
01:17:51,634 --> 01:17:54,970
- <i>TURN AROUND!</i>
<i>TURN AROUND!</i> - <i>ASSHOLE!</i>

1213
01:17:54,971 --> 01:17:58,024
HE'S GOT THE MONEY!
I'M TELLING YOU.

1214
01:17:58,024 --> 01:17:59,558
HE WAS
LYING DOWN, DEAD!

1215
01:17:59,558 --> 01:18:01,893
- <i>WOULD YOU DRIVE?</i>
- I'M DRIVING!

1216
01:18:01,894 --> 01:18:04,863
( both shouting )

1217
01:18:04,864 --> 01:18:07,032
BIG SHIT!
ARE YOU DOING 50?!

1218
01:18:07,033 --> 01:18:08,984
NO, SHE'S FINE.
DRIVE A LITTLE FASTER.

1219
01:18:08,985 --> 01:18:11,203
- <i>STOP YELLING.</i>
- WE JUST SHOT PEOPLE!

1220
01:18:11,203 --> 01:18:13,238
JUST PULL OVER,
LET ME DRIVE.

1221
01:18:13,239 --> 01:18:15,624
- SHE'S NOT DRIVING SLOW.
- PULL OVER, LET ME DRIVE.

1222
01:18:15,624 --> 01:18:17,626
DRIVE OR PULL OVER?
MAKE UP YOUR MIND!

1223
01:18:17,626 --> 01:18:20,712
I WILL DRIVE.
I KNOW THE ROAD. I KNOW THIS GUY.

1224
01:18:20,713 --> 01:18:24,500
I SHOT HIS HAND OFF.

1225
01:18:24,500 --> 01:18:28,003
Lexi:
<i>WHAT THE FUCK SHOULD WE DO?</i> <i>THERE'S A FUCKING COP THERE.</i>

1226
01:18:30,339 --> 01:18:32,591
HAIL MARY, FULL OF GRACE,
THE LORD IS WITH THEE...

1227
01:18:33,893 --> 01:18:36,061
TURN LEFT, LEFT!
FOLLOW HIM.

1228
01:18:36,062 --> 01:18:37,813
FUCK.

1229
01:19:30,900 --> 01:19:32,952
WHAT DO WE HAVE HERE?

1230
01:19:32,952 --> 01:19:35,037
YOU TELL ME.

1231
01:19:35,037 --> 01:19:37,489
I'LL TELL <i>YOU</i> ALONE.

1232
01:19:39,492 --> 01:19:41,660
WHY NOT HERE?

1233
01:19:41,660 --> 01:19:44,713
CAN I TALK TO YOU
IN PRIVATE, PLEASE?

1234
01:19:44,713 --> 01:19:46,998
Both: NO!

1235
01:19:46,999 --> 01:19:49,718
PLEASE.

1236
01:19:49,718 --> 01:19:51,720
- MISHA, NO!
- SURE.

1237
01:19:51,720 --> 01:19:55,724
WHAT IS THERE TO TALK ABOUT?
WE DO YOUR DIRTY WORK AND YOU'RE GONNA GET AWAY WITH IT?

1238
01:19:55,724 --> 01:19:57,142
HOW ABOUT--
GIVE ME THE KEYS?

1239
01:19:57,143 --> 01:19:59,645
- LET ME TALK TO YOU--
- Helena: <i>GIVE US THE KEYS!</i>

1240
01:20:01,647 --> 01:20:04,433
GIVE US THE FUCKING KEYS.

1241
01:20:09,939 --> 01:20:11,941
THANKS.

1242
01:20:13,943 --> 01:20:15,778
LOOK, THIS IS NOT
THE WAY IT SEEMS.

1243
01:20:15,778 --> 01:20:18,664
I WAS GONNA CALL.
YOU WERE GOING TO MEET ME IN MEXICO--

1244
01:20:18,664 --> 01:20:20,332
THE TWO OF US,
LIKE WE TALKED.

1245
01:20:20,332 --> 01:20:22,584
- I PROMISE YOU THAT.
- <i>COME ON, MISHA, LET'S GO.</i>

1246
01:20:22,585 --> 01:20:25,621
- <i>GOT THE MONEY.</i>
- IT'S NOT WHAT YOU THINK. COME WITH ME NOW.

1247
01:20:25,621 --> 01:20:27,923
DO YOU THINK
I WOULD DO THAT?

1248
01:20:27,923 --> 01:20:30,292
<i>( gunshot )</i>

1249
01:20:30,292 --> 01:20:32,460
<i>( gunshot )</i>

1250
01:20:32,461 --> 01:20:34,296
MISHA!

1251
01:20:35,431 --> 01:20:37,933
Misha:
<i>OH, SHIT!</i>

1252
01:20:45,941 --> 01:20:48,443
Lexi:
<i>OH, MY GOD!</i> <i>WATCH OUT FOR THE PEOPLE!</i>

1253
01:20:48,444 --> 01:20:50,446
- <i>( brakes squeal )</i>
- Lexi: <i>WHAT ARE YOU DOING?</i>

1254
01:20:50,446 --> 01:20:53,449
- Helena: <i>JUST WAIT!</i>
- Lexi: <i>WHAT THE FUCK</i> <i>ARE YOU DOING?</i>

1255
01:20:53,449 --> 01:20:55,451
- <i>SHUT UP!</i>
- <i>HURRY!</i>

1256
01:20:57,953 --> 01:20:59,955
COME ON.
COME ON, BABY.

1257
01:20:59,955 --> 01:21:02,290
GOOD BOY, GOOD BOY.

1258
01:21:08,797 --> 01:21:13,301
THAT'S RIGHT.  ONE RED,
OR... REDDISH PURPLE.

1259
01:21:13,302 --> 01:21:15,971
GREAT.  SO BASICALLY
YOU'RE SAYING THE SPICE GIRLS

1260
01:21:15,971 --> 01:21:18,089
CAME IN HERE
AND TOOK $2 MILLION!

1261
01:21:18,090 --> 01:21:20,475
EXCUSE ME.  THANK YOU.
WE'RE SET UP RIGHT HERE.

1262
01:21:20,476 --> 01:21:22,811
Cop:
<i>WE HAVE THE STILLS</i> <i>FROM THE SECURITY VIDEO?</i>

1263
01:21:22,811 --> 01:21:25,697
READY TO GO?
THREE, TWO--

1264
01:21:25,698 --> 01:21:29,168
TV reporter:
<i>In a daring heist,</i> <i>three robbers armed with guns</i>

1265
01:21:29,168 --> 01:21:32,070
<i>apparently surprised</i>
<i>the casino security guards</i>

1266
01:21:32,071 --> 01:21:35,274
and walked off
with some $2 million.

1267
01:21:35,274 --> 01:21:37,526
- OH GOD!
- <i>It has been concluded</i>

1268
01:21:37,526 --> 01:21:40,612
that the robbers had inside
knowledge of the casino...

1269
01:21:40,613 --> 01:21:44,116
- CRAP!
- <i>because they knew exactly</i> <i>how and when to hit...</i>

1270
01:21:44,116 --> 01:21:46,501
- UH, JACK?
- SOON.

1271
01:21:46,502 --> 01:21:48,420
- JACK?
- SOON.

1272
01:21:48,420 --> 01:21:51,840
- JACK!
- SOON! ( moaning )

1273
01:21:51,840 --> 01:21:55,043
- <i>FREEZE!</i>
- ( screaming )

1274
01:21:55,044 --> 01:21:58,547
Jack's voice:
<i>WHILE DETECTIVE McMAHON WAS</i> <i>INVESTIGATING THE SPICE GIRLS,</i>

1275
01:21:58,547 --> 01:22:02,384
<i>I WAS RUNNING FOR MY LIFE.</i>
<i>MY LUCK HAS SOMEWHAT</i> <i>CHANGED THOUGH.</i>

1276
01:22:02,384 --> 01:22:04,886
<i>THANKS TO</i>
<i>AFFIRMATIVE ACTION,</i>

1277
01:22:04,887 --> 01:22:07,890
- <i>I WAS BEING CHASED BY</i>
<i>DUCK-FOOTED OFFICER MILLER.</i> - SON OF A BITCH!

1278
01:22:07,890 --> 01:22:10,776
PIECE OF SHIT!  COME ON!
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

1279
01:22:10,776 --> 01:22:12,778
WHERE IS OCEAN?
I CANNOT FIND OCEAN.

1280
01:22:12,778 --> 01:22:16,281
HOW DO YOU FIND A MARINA
IF THEY DON'T SAY WHERE THE OCEAN IS?

1281
01:22:18,284 --> 01:22:21,287
WHAT IF JACK MEETS US
AT THE MARINA?

1282
01:22:21,287 --> 01:22:23,572
- HE KNOWS ABOUT--
- YOU'RE PARANOID.  JESUS!

1283
01:22:23,572 --> 01:22:26,575
I'M NOT BEING PARANOID.
I'M TELLING YOU. I KNOW HIM.

1284
01:22:28,577 --> 01:22:31,079
Lexi:
MORE LIKE PSYCHIC.

1285
01:22:31,080 --> 01:22:33,415
HOLY FUCK!
THAT'S JACK!

1286
01:22:33,415 --> 01:22:37,085
- SHIT!
- HEY!  HEY!

1287
01:22:40,589 --> 01:22:43,642
<i>I CAN'T BELIEVE THIS</i>
<i>DUCK-FOOTED BITCH RAN ME DOWN.</i>

1288
01:22:43,642 --> 01:22:46,144
<i>AFTER WHAT THESE FUCKING BROADS</i>
<i>HAVE PUT ME THROUGH,</i>

1289
01:22:46,145 --> 01:22:49,598
<i>IT WOULD BE A PLEASURE TO HAVE</i>
<i>SOME GUY SLIP IT TO ME.</i>

1290
01:22:58,357 --> 01:23:00,108
Man:
WHAT THE FUCK?

1291
01:23:12,087 --> 01:23:14,706
Helena:
COME ON, COME ON! WE GOTTA GO!

1292
01:23:14,707 --> 01:23:16,625
Misha:
<i>I CAN'T MOVE.</i>

1293
01:23:16,625 --> 01:23:18,376
WE'LL COME BACK FOR YOU.

1294
01:23:19,712 --> 01:23:22,431
COME ON!

1295
01:23:28,470 --> 01:23:30,472
SHIT!  WOODY!

1296
01:23:30,472 --> 01:23:32,474
- JUST GO!
- I'VE GOT TO GET HIM!

1297
01:23:32,474 --> 01:23:34,359
COME ON, COME ON, BABY.
COME ON.

1298
01:23:35,778 --> 01:23:38,280
OKAY, GOOD DOG.
I'LL COME RIGHT BACK.

1299
01:23:39,281 --> 01:23:41,533
- OW!
